      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed on the FDA centrifugal pump geometry. GCI for the normalized hemolysis index was 3.2% on the fine mesh (12.4M cells). Richardson extrapolation confirms asymptotic convergence. Achieved level meets required level."
