      "rationale": "The Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model is used, consistent with the methodological framework described in the primary reference cited via referencesIdentifier. Sensitivity to model-form constants was assessed via Monte Carlo sampling. Model form selection is justified. Achieved level meets required level."
    },
