    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors have been assessed and achieved levels meet or exceed required levels at the Low assurance tier for MRL 5. Monte Carlo UQ demonstrates that the 95th-percentile NIH prediction remains below the clinical acceptance threshold across all operating conditions. The hemolysis model form is justified by sensitivity analysis. The assessment team concludes that the CFD model has sufficient credibility to support the VAD regulatory submission for the Class III device.",
